had arrived on the Saturday and Sunday,

00:34:58.920 --> 00:35:03.860 position:72%
principally Germans, each possessed of a small
capital, and all ready to proceed instantly

00:35:03.860 --> 00:35:06.270
to the various German settlements
in the interior without staying

00:35:06.270 --> 00:35:07.650
to waste their means in New York.

00:35:07.650 --> 00:35:10.220
The Custom-house officer's
duty was a mere form."

00:35:10.220 --> 00:35:15.970 position:69%
So again, the students have an understanding
of when did exclusion acts take place.

00:35:15.970 --> 00:35:23.900 position:72%
