00:50:34.490 --> 00:50:38.140 position:59%
Or do we need to veer away from this?"

00:50:38.140 --> 00:50:40.820 position:70%
&gt;&gt; I mean, I think you could do some of both.

00:50:40.820 --> 00:50:46.900 position:66%
You know, I think that it's quite possible
to do some direct instruction, you know,

00:50:46.900 --> 00:50:52.800 position:70%
