how would I answer this question?

00:50:56.320 --> 00:50:58.560 position:59%
What does an ideal response look like?

00:50:58.560 --> 00:51:05.950 position:72%
You know, that too often our expert thinking
as teachers remains invisible to our students.

00:51:05.950 --> 00:51:11.270 position:63%
And so more opportunities for us to make
our thinking visible, of thinking aloud

00:51:11.270 --> 00:51:16.500 position:59%
